oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: 10th Anniversary CRS Live at the Ryman
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Ryman Auditorium (Nashville, Tenn.); Ashton, Kassi; Bentley, Dierks; Church, Eric (Singer); Davis, Jordan (Musician); Gill, Vince; Pardi, Jon, 1985-; Little Big Town (Musical group); Maddie & Tae (Musical group); Hootie & the Blowfish (Musical group); Stapleton, Chris (Musician); Urban, Keith, 1967-; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color window card (black on white) announcing the 10th Anniversary of CRS Live at the Ryman featuring Kassi Ashton, Dierks Bentley, Eric Church, Jordan Davis, Travis Denning, Vince Gill, Adam Hambrick, Caylee Hammack, Jon Pardi, Brandon Lay, Little Big Town, Maddie and Tae, Hootie and the Blowfish, Chris Stapleton, and Keith Urban at the Ryman Auditorium on February 14. Poster features metal photoplate of the sponsor logos and the Team UMG logo.
